## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped
- Slash command autocomplete popup — typing "/" triggers a filtered command list with descriptions. Arrow keys navigate, enter/tab selects, esc dismisses. Filters as you type (e.g. "/ru" → /run, /runs).
- Command registry with 30+ slash commands aligned to desktop app navigation (GH#434).
- Commands support both bare ("tree") and prefixed ("/tree") input.
- Unimplemented commands show "not yet implemented" rather than "unknown command".
- /clear command resets session history.
- /help updated with full command reference.

### New files
- `internal/components/autocomplete.go` — reusable autocomplete popup component
- `internal/components/autocomplete_test.go` — tests for filtering, navigation, selection, dismissal
- `internal/app/commands.go` — slash command registry

### Tests
- `go test ./...` — all passing (8 test packages)
